&gt; Link to entry on the Chrome Platform Status 
&gt;
&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://chromestatus.com/feature/5193953788559360?gate=5082928917512192"&gt;https://chromestatus.com/feature/5193953788559360?gate=5082928917512192&lt;/a&gt;
&gt;
&gt; Links to previous Intent discussions 
