&lt;span class="date"&gt;&lt;a href="/search?l=blink-dev@chromium.org&amp;q=date:20250218" rel="nofollow"&gt;Tue, 18 Feb 2025 09:37:00 -0800&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
